track_notes: Hike from the parking area at the Byron Reece Memorial.
track_title: W4C/NG-004 - Blood Mtn via Byron Reece Mem Trail

track_notes: 3.2 mile hike with 1570 feet of EG and 420 feet of EL from Wolf Pen Gap on GA Hwy 180 (34.7640, -83.9524).  There is parking for several cars near the start of Duncan Ridge Rd. Starting across the highway from Duncan Ridge Road, the Duncan Ridge Trail/Coosa Backcountry Trail starts with a steep climb for the first mile followed by some nice ridgeline hiking before descending to Slaughter Gap at 1.9 miles and the intersection with the Coosa Backcountry Trail.  The trail climbs from here to the summit, joining the AT around 2.4 miles.
track_title: W4G/NG-004 - Blood Mtn via Duncan Ridge Trail

track_notes: Blood Mt. hike from end of Slaughter Creek Rd. 2.3 miles, 1300 EG.
